snippet.title: Similar Triangles - MathHelp.com - Geometry Help
snippet.description: For a complete lesson on similar triangles, go to http://www.MathHelp.com - 1000+ online math lessons featuring a personal math teacher inside every lesson! In this lesson, students review the idea that the ratios of the lengths of corresponding sides of similar figures are equal. Students then use this idea to find missing segment lengths in similar figures.
